name: nebulae
summary: A novel and simple framework based on prevalent DL framework and other image processing libs.v0.0.14: unable to assemble DUPLICATE component without name is not allowed but passing existent name is allowed.v0.0.13: allow users to assemble DUPLICATE component without passing name; add RESIZE component; shorten automatically generated component names.v0.0.12: fix wrong implementation on data augmentation; FuelGenerator will keep original image size if width or height is not given.
